[V:6]              z4 | z4 | z4 |
[V:7]              z4 | z4 | z4 |
[V:8]              z4 | z4 | z4 |
%
% ============================================================
% PHRASE 2 (bars 4–6): All 8 voices enter — full homophony
% Texture: Full 8-voice block chords; S1 sings chromatic ^F bar 4
% All inner voices diatonic; original alto ^C replaced with C (diatonic)
% Chords: Gm | F | Am | Dm | Gm | C | Am | F | Am | F | C | F
% ============================================================
%
[V:1]  G F E ^F | G G G F | E F E !fermata!D |
