[V:8]  C, D, A,, D, | C, C, F,, A,, | A,, A,, A,, D, |
%
% ============================================================
% PHRASE 3 (bars 7–9): TTBB choir, SSAA silent
% Texture: 4-voice antiphonal response — rich lower choir
% Melody in T1 following original soprano closely (Bb region)
% Original alto _E (Eb) not present in TTBB; use diatonic E/D neighbors
% Chords: F | Bb | F | F | Bb | F | Bb | F | F | Bb | F | F
% ============================================================
%
[V:1]  z4 | z4 | z4 |
[V:2]  z4 | z4 | z4 |
[V:3]  z4 | z4 | z4 |
[V:4]  z4 | z4 | z4 |
